  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926820/extras/572e48b715aa770c1671aed869fd670c.poster.avif?t=1692298964\" width=530 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926820/extras/572e48b715aa770c1671aed869fd670c.webm?t=1692298964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926820/extras/572e48b715aa770c1671aed869fd670c.mp4?t=1692298964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Eternal Space Battles is a classic wave-based side-scrolling shooter with bullet hell elements. <br><br>- Storm into space battles against more than 20 types of enemies, plus challenging bosses. <br>- Buy new ships and upgrade them to get to the top of the leaderboard.<br>- Complete missions and advance through game levels to earn points and cash! <br>- More than 50 Steam achievements of varying difficulty. <br><br><br>Earth is under attack by alien invaders. The United Earth Forces' High Command has tasked 3 superior battle spaceships, equipped with the latest in human technology, with defeating the aliens' armada. Take control of your ship, and teach that alien scum a lesson! The fate of the universe rests in your hands!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926820/extras/572e48b715aa770c1671aed869fd670c.poster.avif?t=1692298964\" width=530 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926820/extras/572e48b715aa770c1671aed869fd670c.webm?t=1692298964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/926820/extras/572e48b715aa770c1671aed869fd670c.mp4?t=1692298964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Eternal Space Battles is a classic wave-based side-scrolling shooter with bullet hell elements. <br><br>- Storm into space battles against more than 20 types of enemies, plus challenging bosses. <br>- Buy new ships and upgrade them to get to the top of the leaderboard.<br>- Complete missions and advance through game levels to earn points and cash! <br>- More than 50 Steam achievements of varying difficulty. <br><br><br>Earth is under attack by alien invaders. The United Earth Forces' High Command has tasked 3 superior battle spaceships, equipped with the latest in human technology, with defeating the aliens' armada. Take control of your ship, and teach that alien scum a lesson! The fate of the universe rests in your hands!",
